results.title: LIVE fully. LAUGH often. LOVE much. - Cuff Bracelet - pure aluminum, stainless steel, copper, brass or sterling silver cuff - inspirational
results.description:
This light, yet sturdy, 1/4 inch wide cuff bracelet is stamped with "LIVE fully.  LAUGH often.  LOVE much".  

HOW TO ORDER: 

1. Choose your metal choice from the first drop-down menu.   The cuff is available in Pure Aluminum (silver), Stainless Steel (silver), Brass (gold), Copper (like a penny), or Sterling Silver.  All cuffs are solid (not plated).  For more information about our metals, please see below.

2.  Choose your options from the second drop-down menu.   For non-custom designs, choosing “As shown” designates that you would like the cuff sent with the same design in the photo.  “Personalize the back” means that the front of the cuff will be as shown in the photo, but you would also like to add personalization/a hidden message to the inside of the cuff.  Please see more details below regarding personalization and text limits.    

3. If personalization is desired, please enter that information into the text field below the drop-down menus.  On some browsers, you may need to click “Add your personalization” to make the text box visible.   

4. If you are done shopping, please view your cart.  If there is any more information you would like to add, there will be another box at checkout where you can place that information.  Please double check any personalization entered for typos, errors, and autocorrects gone awry and verify your shipping address before submitting your order.  

———————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————

OUR MATERIALS:   

Pure Aluminum/Stainless steel: 

Pure aluminum and stainless steel are generally a safe choice for those with metal allergies, as they’re considered generally hypoallergenic.  They will not tarnish, fade, or change color.  Aluminum is lighter and more flexible/comfortable, while stainless steel is heavier and more rigid.  
     
Brass, Copper, and Sterling Silver:

These metals are all naturally prone to oxidation or tarnish over time. Some environments and body chemistries cause this oxidation to occur more aggressively than others.  We have no way of knowing how the metal will react to your recipient's Ph or environment and these metals may require more maintenance for select individuals to avoid tarnish.  While some people actually love the look of aged metal, if you feel that you or your recipient will not or will not want to have to care for the cuff please choose pure aluminum or stainless steel, which does not require maintenance. Light tarnishing of these metals can be easily removed with the polishing pad included in each purchase of these metals. These pads can also be purchased in the “add-ons” section of our shop if needed.

———————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————

DETAILS: 

The bracelet will be sent with a lightly brushed finish since I feel it makes the bracelet the most legible and wears well. 

The cuff measures 6 inches long before forming, will fit most wrists and can be easily adjusted by gently bending to a comfortable shape.  We do have limited availability of 7" cuffs (for wrists 7-7.5" around) in aluminum ONLY.  Please let us know if this is something you need.  

A personalized message can be added to the back (up to 30 letters, spaces, and symbols) by choosing that option.  This site can help you calculate the number of characters: http://www.lettercount.com/.  Please be sure to follow any text limits regarding your customization requests.  Failure to adhere to these limits may delay your order.   If the text you would like to have stamped will not fit within these limits, please contact us to discuss your options. 

Your gift will be shipped ready to give, tastefully carded, and tucked into a protective poly sleeve.  A gift box with a ribbon and note can be added at checkout if desired.   

While we strive to be as precise as possible, due to the handmade nature of these items they will not have machine-made “perfection”.  EACH design and letter is individually hammered, one strike at a time, BY HAND.  This may lead to some variations in the spacing, depth of the designs, and placement of the letters. This is not to be considered a defect, but instead a part of the unique character of the piece.

All items are shipped via USPS First-Class Mail unless a shipping upgrade is chosen to add faster options.   During high-volume periods (around major gift-giving holidays), we ALWAYS recommend that you use PRIORITY shipping for a few dollars more.  Priority mail is processed more quickly than First-Class (typically delivered in 3 days or less) and includes insurance to cover your purchase from loss or damage during transit.

RUSH guarantees that your item will ship no later than the next BUSINESS day.  If same-day shipping is possible and priority shipping is chosen, we will ship your item the same day.    

GREEN THINKING: Whenever possible, we source our metals and supplies from other domestic small businesses.  When you support us, you also support a whole network of small family-owned businesses here in America.   We recycle/reuse packaging materials to help reduce our environmental impact. Our precious metals (silver, gold and, rose gold-filled) are refined at a reputable American business that is both environmentally and energy responsible. We recycle all acceptable waste/scrap metal to reduce our landfill footprint.   Our standard packaging is completely recyclable.  

Please be aware that the photos shown are simply a representation of previous items I have created and may not be exactly what you receive, as each item is uniquely created just for you at the time you order.

Questions? Contact me through Etsy Convos and I will be happy to help!

We ALWAYS send continuous yardage when available, or if not available, we will contact you prior to shipping!

Colors include white, grey, yellow, black, green and hint of orange.

100% cotton fabric.  Machine wash warm, mild detergent, non-chlorine bleach, tumble dry low, use warm iron.

To see other fabrics we HAVE in this collection go to:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/FabricUtopia?ref=hdr_shop_menu&search_query=Timeless+Treasures+Live+Love+Laugh

As we also sell this fabric in our retail shop, sometimes our inventory is off.  You can leave instructions for us including how you want the order shipped.   This helps avoid any delays that might happen by trying to contact you.  The choices are as follows:

ORDERED AMOUNT ONLY - Cancel the order if you do not have the stated amount in continuous yardage.
SEND WHAT YOU HAVE - Send the amount you have. We will adjust the prices and shipping accordingly.
CONTACT ME - If you do NOT have the exact amount, please contact me for instructions (the default for our shop).
SEE NOTE - Leave any instructions in the customers note section.

CHOOSE YOUR FABRIC LENGTH FROM THE FOLLOWING:
1/4 yards ( 9 inches x 44 inches)
FAT QUARTER (18 inches x 22 inches) 
1/2 yards (18 inches x 44 inches)
3/4 yards (27 inches x 44 inches)
1 yard (36 inches x 44 inches)
1 1/4 yards (45 inches x 44 inches)
1 1/2 yards (54 inches x 44 inches)

The quantity button will allow you to purchase 1/4 yard, 1/2 yard, 3/4 yard, 1 yard, 1-1/4 yard and 1-1/2 yard cuts along with fat quarters. The price is listed next to the size in the drop down menu.   Multiple quantities will be cut in a single continuous piece unless otherwise stated.  Do not order more yardage than what is listed in the drop down box.

Example:  If you wish to purchase 3 yards, select the 1 yard cut from the drop down menu and then a quantity of 3.  You can purchase multiple lengths of the same fabric as long as it does not exceed the total quantity listed on the drop down menu.

Fabric cut sizes are approximate as the width of cotton fabrics vary between 43 and 45 inches.  Fabric is cut with a rotary cutter on a ruled mat to provide you with the straight cuts whenever possible.

If you need a custom listing for a length not listed or would like help in coordinating or calculating yardage for your projects, please convo us or request a custom listing via the custom order button at the top right of this page.  Sometimes we have more fabric in stock than what is listed.   If for some reason we have less fabric than shown, we will contact you for instructions unless otherwise instructed.  

Shipping is via first class mail for up to 2 yards. 3 to 8 yards ship via a priority flat rate envelope.   We use calculated shipping based on weight, and offer "FREE" domestic Priority Mail shipping on orders higher orders, this will be displayed when ordering..  Shipping upgrades and international rates are available at check-out.  If a significant overcharge in shipping happens due to a combined or multiple yard purchase, it will be refunded to you.   When buying multiple quantities of small fabric yardage shipping prices can be off and force priority mail prices before needed.   Please let us know if you wish first class shipping in this case.

We try to show multiple images of each fabric.  The first is usually from the Manufacturer or supplier.  The second displays a ruler so that you can get an idea of the size of the fabric design and pattern.  Others are usually close ups or project ideas.   NOTE:  Sometimes the pictures we take vary in color from the manufacturer's picture due to cameras, lighting and other factors.  In most cases, the first image will be the most accurate in displaying the true color(s).

results.title: American Psycho Cross Stitch Pattern, Patrick Bateman, cross stitch pdf, horror cross stitch, Halloween, modern cross stitch, funny
results.description:
You like Huey Lewis and the News? 

This listing is for an instant PDF (adobe reader) download, no kits or materials will be sent to you.

Floss: DMC, recommended, but includes Anchor to DMC Embroidery Floss Conversion.
(Conversion colors are just a suggestion, do to variance in color please check the colors against an official DMC/Anchor color card. For best results use the colors listed.)

Fabric: Aida 14-count, recommended
(Can be stitched on other Aida counts, evenweave and linen, finished size will vary depending on Aida count)


Your PDF download includes:
• Full color chart with symbols.
• Black and white chart with symbols for easy printing (i.e. printer ink is expensive yo, I got your back).
• DMC thread color key (with DMC to Anchor Conversion).
• Estimate of skeins needed based on number of stitches used.

This is an instant PDF download. Due to the electronic nature of this pattern, all sales are final.

Patterns are original designs and should not be redistributed in any format. For personal use only, unless otherwise noted.

Please contact me with any questions or concerns. Please don't contact me if you're trying to get a reservation at Dorsia .

Once payment is confirmed your files will be available to download. Please follow the instructions in the link https://www.etsy.com/help/article/3949.
